@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zdzunt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(0.99)
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.63 / v1 + 0.81)) + (0.93 / 0.98))
    v0 = (wp.cos(v1) * (0.68 / (tmp + 0.08 * v2 + 0.45)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.22)) + ((v2 + 0.21 / v0 + 0.24) / v2))
    v2 = 0.34
    v0 = (v2 + wp.exp(0.50))
    data[tid] = v0
